81c1b9b9f686f4f3394c0b4b8953b06511df7c445692963fc6124249604f5dfb36b205b6d4be89957bf6ca129d3149726046009a79a6924b594d7327925b43c9  0001-setup-disk-fix-hang-with-UEFI-and-interactive-none.patch
"
